name: PachiPara 3D - Ooumi Monogatari 2 with Agnes Lum - Pachi-Pro Fuuunroku Hana Kesareta License [3DS]
description:
[English]

In this game take the role of Ash Ville, an evil driving examiner and fail the student by sabotaging traffic signs and lights.

[日本語]

運転試験官の悪魔のアッシュ・ヴィルとして、ドライバーを落ちさせるために標識や信号を妨害するゲームです。

Made by José Fonseca and Melissa Cebola during Exaud's internship
